{"tid":1623303,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人公司同我公司一樣開始扣大假","createTime":"2019-10-04T19:41:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T04:14:56.000Z","uid":220705,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"0bb8f7e9b0ea09af606ec6bb7da89e55e12cf062","tid":1623303,"uid":220705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T19:41:37.000Z","msg":"我做橙色戲院前線<br />\n公司由1/10起如果因為商場停業而關門就要去其他分店幫手<br />\n如果唔係就扣大假扣糧<br />\n我地心諗地鐵都無 返完工都未車返屋企啦 個個被逼要扣為左返到屋企<br />\n係呢個時勢先黎搾壓員工 有冇第間公司好似我果間咁撚仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><del><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><br />\nP.S.前線外寫字樓全撚部都係藍</span></del></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46760d0839a232480900712f266db694d477fc75","tid":1623303,"uid":70417,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T19:47:39.000Z","msg":"睇合約，合約冇寫你有權話超出工作範圍<br />\n不過通常都有寫"},{"pid":"a5da072578de31f3d3513ca7dfa94c0ff69ca77a","tid":1623303,"uid":220705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"46760d0839a232480900712f266db694d477fc75","tid":1623303,"uid":70417,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T19:47:39.000Z","msg":"睇合約，合約冇寫你有權話超出工作範圍<br />\n不過通常都有寫"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T19:53:03.000Z","msg":"我諗佢都係合法先做得出<br />\n不過佢懶係好心講俾我地聽<br />\n話仲有得選擇扣唔扣已經好好果下真係嬲到震 <br />\n不如直接扣鳩我叫我咪返工算啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"462fc233bfdffb6288ebd0d53957f4b85c25d737","tid":1623303,"uid":173528,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T21:09:37.000Z","msg":"同某K字頭化妝品公司一樣，<br />\n如果返開嗰間分店開唔到既話就會調去其他地區返，<br />\n或者扣鐘扣例假、大假扣糧。<br />\n呢排仲係咁炒人<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c78335d9c3c136aa1a25f30c72096a98239033f","tid":1623303,"uid":220705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"462fc233bfdffb6288ebd0d53957f4b85c25d737","tid":1623303,"uid":173528,"like":1,"dislike":0,"s